works.description:
This is Satru Nashak Shankh (Shankh to  
Destroy Enemies) If you have trouble with enemies, they are making problem
 
in life, business and job also giving curse and doing tantra prayog for
you  
and they are doing best to destroy you completely and you are helpless or 

innocent, you are suffering from enemies attack but not able to do
anything  
so easily place this shankh at home and daily show mustard oil lamp to  
shankh also show dhoop and incense sticks. If this shankh is available in 

your home or in office and you are doing worship for it properly so in  
whole life any enemies cannot harm you physically, mentally or
spiritually.  
Even this shankh will destroy them completely within some days. This item 

has natural god gifted power, no need to do anything special for it. Only 

do regular worship and pray for protection and to destroy enemies. Within 

some days you will feel changes in situation and all enemies who are known
 
or unknown, they will be destroyed. Its guaranteed solution for enemies.
